WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.834
You never said
you knew Johnny Fontane!

00:00:03.040 --> 00:00:06.874
- Sure. You want to meet him?
- Great! Sure.

00:00:07.080 --> 00:00:10.789
- My father helped him with his career.
- He did?

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.956
How?

00:00:13.720 --> 00:00:16.871
- Let's listen to this song.
- Michael...

